與您同心同行！<br />\n<br />\n香港工會聯合會<br />\n<br />\n所有工聯會會員都收到嘅感謝短訊&uarr;。"},{"pid":"3b19959b45ff6138392a230f453044bf479e18d5","tid":1754690,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c71f5f1a5e5c2cd2912c436671fddea1165c86","tid":1754690,"uid":47521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f9224938a90815bf1a0faa298450a59c3799a1","tid":1754690,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:06:09.000Z","msg":"又點呀大師兄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT2rspd8gyX3LO5RT7oYoq1KUh-D9QIQzGxtkWGGUBq2DYsNZru\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcT2rspd8gyX3LO5RT7oYoq1KUh-D9QIQzGxtkWGGUBq2DYsNZru&h=8c36726b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSMAVkP7nfj_GAMXXaSqLGKQmeM3wBclEobp3c1M2WF0baIzE34\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSMAVkP7nfj_GAMXXaSqLGKQmeM3wBclEobp3c1M2WF0baIzE34&h=d3b593be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRgehwUjaX4O3xi4BVFuyGjj1FVgEVPyhSdArVPXgi92arjiSDV\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRgehwUjaX4O3xi4BVFuyGjj1FVgEVPyhSdArVPXgi92arjiSDV&h=f78b4f05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe46629a6038b1bb9e24bf8205dcb8f2345a3c22","tid":1754690,"uid":185606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"講黑色恐怖，真係所有人都唔夠工聯會講<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AQTybP.jpg\" data-thum